The paper deals with image enhancement and classification using statistical features and machine learning techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.MM) sub-categories. The use of optimization frameworks and statistical features also suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
